author: @cynthiabeltran1680
content: An incredible tribute and performance. Madonna looks stunning. This is what admirers love about a pop ballerina: Stage presence... Madonna is the owner of the stage. She looks better than in 2008. I missed this image so much then! Live to tell, my favourite song... Always. Thank you!!! ❤❤❤
